{
  "stem": "14708.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I went to the door and put my hand on the shoulder of one of these detectives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said, oh, yes, miss.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Please, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went to that street where we talked-- what we arranged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I waited two hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was 100% sure that they took Jan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Finally, finally after two hours, he came from a completely different direction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He said that first of all, he had to wait a long time because the restaurant was full, so until the waiter came and he could pay.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then he didn't know whether these people are not following me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So he didn't want to take the same route.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So he went half the city around and around until finally, he got there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So this was-- I think during those two hours, I decided that I will marry him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's a very important two hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then on October 15, 1944, the Hungarian Arrow Cross Party, which was a Hungarian variant of the swastika, the Hungarian fascists, they, they took over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The Germans arrested the Regent Horthy and his son.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the fascists took over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then it started in earnest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It became an extremely, extremely dangerous time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then they started to build the ghetto in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The thing was that the Germans didn't have time any more to deport the Jews from Budapest, because the Soviet army was too close.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So they put them in ghettos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The men and some of the woman were-- went also to labor camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But there was always a possibility to take everybody on foot to Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Austria was not yet occupied or liberated, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So this, this was a terrible time.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
